Roscoe CHAMBERS, Petitioner,
v.
William HARDY, et al.
No. 19-8252.
Supreme Court of the United States.
May 18, 2020
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
